title: Studio in Midtown East. No Broker Fee!
posting_body: ['Please note: This is not available for a short term rental.', '12 month leases only!', 'Amenities: No Pets, No Laundry, Hardwood Floors, Street Parking, No Dishwasher, High CeilingsVideo Tour:\xa0https://youtu.be/yXjCVHZHgRs', 'Only 5 blocks to the E M trains!', '$2,195', 'cash Lease Signing Bonus =', 'you pay per month $2,712 (Gross rent is $2,895)', '.', 'We are looking for long term tenants.', 'If you pay your rent on time and take care of the property we will want you to stay and keep the rent within your budget.', 'Large and Sunny Studio located in the heart of Midtown East.', 'Steps from multiple train lines, laundromat, shops, galleries, restaurants, lounges, cafes, etc.', 'Priced to rent immediately.', 'If interested contact right away to schedule a viewing before it goes.', 'Requirements', '1.', 'Everyone on lease has a combined annual income of at least $107,000.', '2.', 'Everyone on lease has a credit score of at least 690.', '3.', 'Or you have a guarantor(s) with credit score(s) of at least 700 and combined annual income of at least $145,000.', '4.', 'Or you have savings of 4 months worth of rent or more']
